name: Fibonaccio
description:
This is our entry for the Geta Game Jam, we had a lot of fun making this!

As the theme was "It never ends" we decided to make a puzzle game... that never ends. There are 11 different puzzles that can be completed in random order.

Music composed by the We Were Here series music composer :)
https://www.linkedin.com/in/leonvanderstel/

All assets are made by us, except for the buttons, we downloaded those for free from: https://www.kenney.nl/ Awesome guy!
